'''Microsoft HoloLens'''（“[[全息|全息]][[透镜|透镜]]”）是[[微软|微软]]在[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]上推出的一个[[智能眼鏡|智能眼鏡]]產品，是[[Windows_Holographic|Windows Holographic]]使用的主要设备。它采用先进的传感器、全角度高清晰3D光学透镜[[头戴式显示器|头戴式显示器]]以及環繞音效，允许在[[增强现实|增强现实]]中用户界面可以与用户透過眼神、语音和手势互相交流<ref name="Restart">{{cite web|last1=Hempel|first1=Jessi|title=Restart: Microsoft in the age of Satya Nadella|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/01/microsoft-nadella/|publisher=Wired|accessdate=22 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|quote=Each lens has three layers of glass—in blue, green, and red—full of microthin corrugated grooves that diffract light. […] A “light engine” above the lenses projects light into the glasses, where it hits the grating and then volleys between the layers of glass millions of times.|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130193049/https://www.wired.com/2015/01/microsoft-nadella/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>参见：[[全息光学元件|全息光学元件]], [[衍射光栅|衍射光栅]]</ref>其开发代号为“Project Baraboo”。HoloLens由微软在2015年1月21日公布，在此之前已经开发了5年之久，其构想的一部分成为了在2010年发布的[[Kinect|Kinect]]。<ref name="Wired hands-on">{{cite web|last1=Hempel|first1=Jessi|title=Project HoloLens: Our Exclusive Hands-On With Microsoft’s Holographic Goggles|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/01/microsoft-hands-on/|website=Wired|accessdate=22 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125090328/http://www.wired.com/2015/01/Microsoft-hands-on|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Restart" />。

微软展示了HoloLens的各种应用，包括HoloStudio (一个3D建模软件)，可以输出成为适用于3D打印机的模型；Holobuilder，其灵感来自于电子游戏《[[當個創世神|當個創世神]]》；[[Skype|Skype]]；OnSight，在与[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]喷气推进实验室（JPL）的合作中开发的软件工具。<ref name="Engadget hands-on">{{cite web|last1=Gilbert|first1=Ben|title=I experienced 'mixed reality' with Microsoft's holographic computer headset, 'HoloLens'|url=http://www.engadget.com/2015/01/21/microsoft-hololens-hands-on/|website=Engadget|accessdate=22 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202050404/https://www.engadget.com/2015/01/21/microsoft-hololens-hands-on/|dead-url=no}}</ref>OnSight将来自[[好奇号|好奇号]]火星车的数据整合为火星环境的3D模拟，使得科学家们能够使用HoloLens设备对其观看、交互和协作。OnSight可以用于任务规划，能够观察模拟中的目标，用手势拉动，并选择菜单命令对火星车的活动进行编程。<ref name="JPL">{{cite web|title=NASA, Microsoft Collaboration Will Allow Scientists to "Work on Mars"|url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4451|publisher=Jet Propulsion Laboratory|accessdate=22 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108185253/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4451|dead-url=no}}</ref>JPL计划在好奇号的任务操作中部署OnSight，在2015年7月时将其用于控制火星车。<ref name="livestream">{{cite AV media |people=Terry Myerson, Alex Kipman, Jeff Norris, Satya Nadella |date=21 January 2015 |title=Windows 10: The Next Chapter |medium= |url=https://ll.ms-studiosmedia.com/events/2015/1501/Windows10CP/live/Windows10CP.html |access-date=22 January 2015 |format= |time=01:36:53 |location= |publisher=Microsoft |archive-date=2015-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412031218/https://ll.ms-studiosmedia.com/events/2015/1501/Windows10CP/live/Windows10CP.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

HoloLens使用的传感器是一种高效节能的深度摄像头，具有120°×120°的视野。<ref name="Wired hands-on" />传感器提供的其他功能包括头部跟踪，视频拍摄，以及声音捕捉。除了高性能的[[CPU|CPU]]和[[GPU|GPU]]，HoloLens带有[[全息处理器|全息处理器]]（HPU）这一协处理器用于从所述的各种传感器集成数据，并处理诸如空间映射，手势识别和语音识别的任务。<ref>参见：[[Sensor_Hub|Sensor Hub]]</ref>

微软预计HoloLens会在2016年确定价格并提供给企业市场和消费市场。<ref name="Verge">{{cite web |last=Shaban |first=Hamza |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7867593/microsoft-announces-windows-holographic |title=Microsoft announces Windows Holographic with HoloLens headset |publisher=The Verge |date=2014-09-02 |accessdate=2015-01-21 |archive-date=2015-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122011759/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7867593/microsoft-announces-windows-holographic |dead-url=no }}</ref>

